The 'mutation catalyst' also seems to produce negative values. Focus on creating grown, two-environment hybrids to maximize points without going negative.

Avoid using the mutation catalyst, as it drastically reduces item value. Do not apply the growth serum to already combined items, as it typically reduces their value.

message: Always use the growth serum on all individual ingredients first. It adds value based on size: small (+5), medium (+10), large (+15). Once all items are grown, combine two *single* grown items. Prioritize combining large items (e.g., large + large, or large + medium) as these yield the highest positive values (up to 35). Do NOT combine items that are already combined (e.g., a hybrid with another hybrid), as this leads to severely negative values. Avoid the mutation catalyst entirely, as it seems to reduce value significantly. When you have a combined item with a good score (30-35), submit to secure your points.
